               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0108GKM">Mäḵodʿä Dabra Gannat Kidāna Mǝḥrat /
                           GKM</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1872" notAfter="1876">King Yoḥannǝs IV (r. 1872-89) is
                        mentioned on <locus target="#15">15</locus> and in Additio 2; Metropolitan
                        ʾAtnatewos (in tenure 1869-76) is also mentioned in Additio 2 and on <locus target="#16r">16r</locus>.</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer (s. Additio 4, the
                     supplication formula on 3r). Probably, the Ms. was
                     previously owned by a certain Walda Śǝllāse (he and the members of his family
                     Fǝśśǝḥa Giyorgis and Walatta Mikāʾel are mentioned in Additio 3 and
                     supplications on 2vb, 35ra-rb). Another name,
                     Gabra Giworgis, is mentioned on 1r (s.
                     Varia).</provenance></history>
